          <div id="review_7685712_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  据译者的译后记，这本书英文版有1120页，现在翻译成中文也有八百多页，分量颇重。前前后后总共读了两个多礼拜，到今天才告一段落。 首先应该感谢一下李康老师的译笔，干脆利落，文字可读。个人接触社会学未深，遇此教材、遇此译者，都是幸运。 再说内容。全书中的模块虽多，但...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7685712_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7685712_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5022554">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5022554/" class="title-link">很现实，很有用！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5022554"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/42015805/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42015805-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/42015805/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">团子Pki</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-07-13"
      class="main-meta">2011-07-13 20:40:54</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5022554_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本书不是那么理论强的让你什么也看不懂，而是用平实的语言，举出大量的例子！从书中可以学到很多现实的问题，而不是空洞的定力！这才是教科书应该的样子！从书里可以了解到社会学方方面面，对于实际生活中遇到的问题有很强的指导作用！非常好！

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5022554/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5022554_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5022554_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





